snippet.title: SM64 Stellato (Savestateless)
snippet.description:
Hello! This was my live playthrough of SM64 Stellato by Itsri and Rulu.

Review: This hack was a pretty enjoyable casual hack till the very last level where it became a kaizo hack for literally 0 reason. Choked reds 11 times at 7/8 reds because of fire spitter QSLGS. Would have been a very good hack without that level in it. DON'T PUT KAIZO LEVELS IN YOUR CASUAL HACKS.

Streamed Live at: https://www.twitch.tv/ozsef
My Romhacking.com Page: https://romhacking.com/user/Ozsef
